# Eval isolation manifest

What a blind subagent receives vs what exists on disk.

## Allowed context

- `eval/scenarios/<id>/prompt.txt` — only user message
- `skill/SKILL.md` + files linked from it
- `projects/out-of-thin-air/**` — full project tree

## Disallowed for blind runs

- Repo root `AGENTS.md`
- Other monorepo projects
- Prior chat / conversation history

## Portable CLI

Eval agents should `cd projects/out-of-thin-air` and use the local
`Justfile` (`just run`, `just hardware`, …) OR monorepo `oota *`
if running from repo root. Skill documents both.

## Metrics

| Metric | Tool |
|--------|------|
| Checkpoint pass rate | `oota eval score <id>` |
| Reference POC | `oota validate` |
| Agent step count | transcript / manual |
